==Azerbaijani==
===Etymology===
From {{inh|az|trk-pro|-}}, whence {{cog|hu|gyárt||to manufacture}}. The root is probably a derivation of {{der|az|trk-pro|*yara||be good enough, be sufficient, be successful}}, appended with the causative suffix ''-t''.
Cognate with {{cog|tr|yaratmak}},
{{cog|uz|yaratmoq}},
{{cog|ky|жаратыл||to be created}},
{{cog|kk|жарату}},
{{cog|ba|яратыу}},
{{cog|tt|яратучы||creator}},
{{cog|ug|ياراتماق}}.
Surface analysis {{suf|az|yaramaq|t}}.
